SUMMARY:Orbitals (Nintendo Switch 2)
DESCRIPTION:Team up as Maki and Omura\, two inseparable explorers with a wh
 ole lot more determination than experience. You’ll brave the perils of spa
 ce in search of help for their crumbling station home\, now trapped within
  a supernatural cosmic storm.\n\nOrbitals captures the warmth and style of
  classic Japanese anime\, brought to life with hand-crafted cinematic cuts
 cenes from Studio Massket\, full Japanese and English voice acting\, and a
 n original soundtrack that channels the magic of the era.\n\nBuilt from th
 e ground up for asymmetric 2-player co-op\, either in local split-screen o
 r online\, Orbitals rewards smart teamwork and clear communication. Use ea
 ch character’s unique tools to open the path forward\, overcome danger\, a
 nd meet out-of-this-world creatures and characters on a bombastic adventur
 e.\n\nhttps://www.igdb.com/games/orbitals--1
END:VEVENT
