 nes\, clarifying certain plot points\, such as Riku's journey and foreshad
 owing of Kingdom Hearts II\, were included\, but no new dialogue was recor
 ded. A gameplay option allows the player to skip cutscenes. The optional b
 osses are included\, along with a new fight against "Unknown Man."\n\nhttp
